    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make a Spot check to assess the target's condition (as per the Keirigan ability) to gain a +2 bonus to attack rolls against the target, and you can lower your Keirigan bonus by any amount (to no lower than 0) to gain the same amount as a weapon damage bonus against the target. If you have the Destruction Mark feat, you can apply it on your next attack against the target. A failed Spot check still grants a +2 bonus to your attack rolls for your next attack.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step grants a +1 bonus to the Spot check. The fifth step lets you use this technique as a Swift action once per encounter, at a cost of 6 Chakra.</p>\n",
